snippet.title: Super Mario Odyssey - Nintendo Switch Presentation 2017 Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mario Odyssey sees Mario leave the Mushroom Kingdom to go on a new sandbox-style journey! Available Now exclusively on Nintendo Switch!

Learn more about Super Mario Odyssey! http://supermario.nintendo.com/
